companyName: ETF Series Solutions Trust - Gadsden Dynamic Multi-Asset ETF
description:
The investment seeks total return.
 The fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing (i) approximately 80% of its total assets with exposure to a variety of asset classes, geographies, and market capitalizations generally based on a long-term view of macroeconomic factors and (ii) approximately 20% of its total assets to add or reduce exposure to one or more asset classes generally based on a short-term view of the market. It may invest in futures contracts to gain long or short exposure to one or more asset classes.
